238
00:31:59,121 --> 00:32:03,321
<i>Nearly half a million come back here
each year to raise their young.</i>

239
00:32:12,241 --> 00:32:14,881
<i>Adults share parenting duties,</i>

240
00:32:14,961 --> 00:32:17,921
<i>returning every few days
